{"tid":1360576,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"[PrayforKyoani]京阿尼事件援助方法資訊整合POST","createTime":"2019-07-24T11:21:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T03:25:30.000Z","uid":182197,"like":24,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"08093716a2e81f08338fc69e5b58f4b48d29cb9e","tid":1360576,"uid":182197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T11:21:00.000Z","msg":"<strong>官方援助方式</strong><br />\n1.【京都動畫官方捐款資料公佈】(Cr to ACGer)<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.kyotoanimation.co.jp/information/?id=3075\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.kyotoanimation.co.jp%2Finformation%2F%3Fid%3D3075&d=ye2s6s2DGg0XurdvegCh9QVY%2FuVTJuRH1wmMvp6vMc0%3D&h=498ef71e\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.kyotoanimation.co.jp/information/?id=3075</a><br />\n這個是京都動畫因應縱火案接受外間捐款設立的銀行戶口，是最直接支持京阿尼的正式官方渠道，即使是日本國外的民眾也能透過銀行進行國際匯款<br />\n<br />\n關於如何捐款至這個官方銀行戶口，可以google&quot;國際匯款&quot;參考<br />\n<br />\n銀行名 京都信用金庫<br />\n銀行コード 1610<br />\n支店名 南桃山支店<br />\n店番号 048<br />\n口座種別 当座預金<br />\n口座番号 0002890<br />\n口座名義 株式会社京都アニメーション 代表取締役 八田英明<br />\n※ 表示名「ｶ)ｷﾖｳﾄｱﾆﾒｰｼﾖﾝ」<br />\n<br />\nBANK NAME : THE KYOTO SHINKIN BANK<br />\nSWIFT : KYSBJPJZ<br />\nBRANCH NAME : MINAMI MOMOYAMA BRANCH<br />\nBRANCH NUMBER : 048<br />\nADDRESS : 16-50, YOSAI, MOMOYAMA-CHO, HUSHIMI-KU, KYOTO-SHI, KYOTO-HU, 612-8016 , JAPAN<br />\nACCOUNT NUMBER : 0002890<br />\nACCOUNT HOLDER : KYOTO ANIMATION CO.,LTD., REPRESENTATIVE DIRECTOR, HATTA HIDEAKI<br />\n<br />\n2. 《一點微小的幫助》京阿尼網路商店購買教學 (Cr to A Jie)<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-2YKJBqJjZg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D-2YKJBqJjZg&d=ye2s6s2DGg0XurdvegCh9QVY%2FuVTJuRH1wmMvp6vMc0%3D&h=bc832b83\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-2YKJBqJjZg</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>非官方援助方式</strong><br />\n3. Help KyoAni Heal: <a href=\"https://www.gofundme.com/f/help-kyoani-heal\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gofundme.com%2Ff%2Fhelp-kyoani-heal&d=ye2s6s2DGg0XurdvegCh9QVY%2FuVTJuRH1wmMvp6vMc0%3D&h=3c975ace\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.gofundme.com/f/help-kyoani-heal</a><br />\n由京阿尼既海外發行商發起既眾籌<br />\n<br />\n4. Share Your Message of Support With Kyoto Animation: <a href=\"https://www.crunchyroll.com/anime-news/2019/07/18-1/share-your-message-of-support-with-kyoto-animation\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.crunchyroll.com%2Fanime-news%2F2019%2F07%2F18-1%2Fshare-your-message-of-support-with-kyoto-animation&d=ye2s6s2DGg0XurdvegCh9QVY%2FuVTJuRH1wmMvp6vMc0%3D&h=e530ba80\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.crunchyroll.com/anime-news/2019/07/18-1/share-your-message-of-support-with-kyoto-animation</a><br />\nViolet Evergarden教識大家,請唔好睇小文字既力量,你簡單既心意都好重要<br />\n<br />\n5. 京阿尼大火在港悼念活動籌備: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/mourning.kyoani.hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fmourning.kyoani.hk%2F&d=ye2s6s2DGg0XurdvegCh9QVY%2FuVTJuRH1wmMvp6vMc0%3D&h=26c02eb1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/mourning.kyoani.hk/</a><br />\n<br />\n6. 日本Animate設立左籌款箱,在日巴絲可透過Animate捐款<br />\n<br />\n歡迎補充<br />\n--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n小小感想想講好耐,<br />\n與其係到諗京阿尼到底要用幾耐重建,可唔可以真係重新振作,<br />\n倒不如諗下方法點幫依家處於悲傷既受難員工同家屬<br />\n事件發生至今,我最大既感受係無力感同罪惡感<br />\n無力係因為我知道無論我捐幾多錢,有D野都永遠返唔到黎,<br />\n罪惡係覺得明明人地帶左咁多野俾我,但自己金錢上既付出係完全唔對等,<br />\n如果佢地有多D收入,會唔會可以有多個保安?會唔會有好D既保安系統?會唔會可能,可能令今次悲劇有少少既變化?<br />\n但我更清楚,再諗都無用,有用既係,係到呼籲大家幫手,少少益善,多多無拘<br />\n如果你無能力,都可以透過方法(4)表達你既支持,或者將以上資訊share出去,最好就send俾D圈內KOL(youtuber, etc)請佢地都share埋出去<br />\n仲有好多野想講,但小弟作為毒撚不擅辭令,以下影片基本上講左我想講既野<br />\nAn Open Letter To Kyoto Animation (Cr to Under The Scope): <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=fuAxFe-BB-8&amp;list=LL2iSNeu0SeK-Bg1syJwVumw&amp;index=2&amp;t=0s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DfuAxFe-BB-8%26list%3DLL2iSNeu0SeK-Bg1syJwVumw%26index%3D2%26t%3D0s&d=ye2s6s2DGg0XurdvegCh9QVY%2FuVTJuRH1wmMvp6vMc0%3D&h=d5500f9b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=fuAxFe-BB-8&amp;list=LL2iSNeu0SeK-Bg1syJwVumw&amp;index=2&amp;t=0s</a><br />\nThank you Kyoani"},{"pid":"855863e56bd4ebe29a0e9b33de92f2d740fcd388","tid":1360576,"uid":182197,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T11:21:46.000Z","msg":"我會推至少一個星期,希望多D人睇到"},{"pid":"969f85be53e813389bf559bf93a8e9b1b42b8c36","tid":1360576,"uid":45373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T11:43:05.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"fcf19a75de95420e83c2a340d44b27a55f679902","tid":1360576,"uid":182197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T12:06:20.000Z","msg":"Gigguk: Thank You Kyoto Animation.<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=bTl0BBrw3Y0&amp;t=1s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DbTl0BBrw3Y0%26t%3D1s&d=ye2s6s2DGg0XurdvegCh9QVY%2FuVTJuRH1wmMvp6vMc0%3D&h=401b960b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=bTl0BBrw3Y0&amp;t=1s</a>"},{"pid":"3fd2a9f3ab58137c1e6992fcc5eda088856a3c73","tid":1360576,"uid":182197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:32:44.000Z","msg":"push before sleep"},{"pid":"edc9ca30456b5449dbc56eb49fc4f707cabf2f8c","tid":1360576,"uid":2223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:43:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ba6bb92733bf8358ee74f458a05f3fabeb65a95e","tid":1360576,"uid":182197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T18:15:17.000Z","msg":"小小補充關於電匯費用<br />\nIf you are sending any mount lower than 4000 JPY you may want to consider passing money to a local funding gathering you can trust. According to the bank, 2000 JPY handling fee applies per international transfer. Any thing less than 4000 JPY is half. <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.kyoto-shinkin.co.jp/personal/deposit_investment/foreigncurrency/pdf/gaika2-005.pdf\" 